PN,38801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1778512268
OL,3,CUnexploded WWII bombs to remain buried
OL,4,Cnear residential development
OL,6,FFour unexploded World War Two bombs in
OL,7,FGuernsey will remain buried close to a
OL,8,Fresidential development in St Peter
OL,9,FPort, officials have decided.
OL,11,FIt follows an year-long consultation
OL,12,Fbetween the island's Committee for
OL,13,FHome Affairs and experts from the UK's
OL,14,FMinistry of Defence.
OL,16,FThe bombs are buried eight metres
OL,17,Funderground in Le Foulon - close to a
OL,18,Fresidential development at Wellington
OL,19,FClose.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1778512268
OL,3,CUnexploded WWII bombs to remain buried
OL,4,Cnear residential development
OL,6,FThe Ministry of Defence's
OL,7,Finvestigation found they were
OL,8,Foriginally dropped from a British
OL,9,Fbomber following an aborted raid on
OL,10,FGerman naval vessels off the coast of
OL,11,FFrance during the war
OL,13,FSince pilots were emptying aircraft -
OL,14,Frather than carrying out targeted
OL,15,Fraids - experts concluded that they
OL,16,Fwere not likely to have been armed
OL,17,Fwhen they fell.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1778512268
OL,3,CUnexploded WWII bombs to remain buried
OL,4,Cnear residential development
OL,6,FThe government say the decision to
OL,7,Fleave them in place was made on the
OL,8,Fbasis of two points highlighted in the
OL,9,FMinistry of Defence's report:
OL,11,FThe bombs are two thousand pound
OL,12,Farmour piercing bomb, designed to
OL,13,Fpenetrate hardened targets and then
OL,14,Fexplode after that.
OL,16,FEach one is more than six foot long
OL,17,Fwith a tail fin on top.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1778512268
OL,3,CUnexploded WWII bombs to remain buried
OL,4,Cnear residential development
OL,6,FKevin Murphy, Channel Islands
OL,7,FEmergency Planning Officer said the
OL,8,Finvestigation has created a lot of
OL,9,Fchallenges.
OL,11,FHe said: "Most of the time the
OL,12,Fmilitary will deal with a single piece
OL,13,Fof ordnance and they're very used to
OL,14,Fthat - the issues we have with four
OL,15,Fpieces of ordnance very close together
OL,16,Fis very much that people are concerned
OL,17,Fabout sympathetic detonation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1778512268
OL,3,CUnexploded WWII bombs to remain buried
OL,4,Cnear residential development
OL,6,F"If one goes off unexpectedly, how is
OL,7,Fthat going to affect the others and
OL,8,Fall these kinds of questions, the
OL,9,Fcomplexities of it, we've asked our
OL,10,Fmilitary experts and we've luckily got
OL,11,Fall of the answers that we needed to
OL,12,Ftry to resolve this as safely as we
OL,13,Fcan."
OL,15,FDeputy Mark Leadbeater, President of
OL,16,Fthe Committee for Home Affairs says he
OL,17,Fis very happy with the decision.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1778512268
OL,3,CUnexploded WWII bombs to remain buried
OL,4,Cnear residential development
OL,6,F"We're safe in the knowledge that they
OL,7,Fare highly unlikely to be armed and
OL,8,Feven if they were armed, the fuses
OL,9,Fthat they've got on there are not the
OL,10,Ftype of fuses that can degrade over
OL,11,Ftime and pose a risk, so I'm satisfied
OL,12,Fthat everyone in the surrounding area
OL,13,Fof Le Foulon should feel safe in the
OL,14,Fknowledge that nothing's going to
OL,15,Fhappen to them."
OL,17,FLocal bomb disposal expert Ben
OL,18,FRemfrey, who has repeatedly called for
OL,19,Faction to be taken to remove the
OL,20,Fbombs, says he remains unconvinced.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1778512268
OL,3,CUnexploded WWII bombs to remain buried
OL,4,Cnear residential development
OL,6,FHe said: "The States, through
OL,7,Fconsultation have made a decision and
OL,8,FI have to honour that, however, it's
OL,9,Fout of my hands now and it's now a
OL,10,Fdecision that I've made and it's not a
OL,11,Fdecision that I would have made.
OL,13,F"My role would be to make sure that
OL,14,Fany probability or risk is removed
OL,15,Ftotally and unfortunately that will
OL,16,Fremain for years to come."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1778512268
OL,3,CUnexploded WWII bombs to remain buried
OL,4,Cnear residential development
OL,6,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for the
OL,7,FMinistry of Defence said: "The MoD has
OL,8,Fprovided support and advice to the
OL,9,FStates of Guernsey throughout this
OL,10,Foperation. Our aim has been to enable
OL,11,Fto the States of Guernsey to make
OL,12,Finformed decisions and ensure public
OL,13,Fsafety. The MoD has, and will continue
OL,14,Fto supply, timely expertise and
OL,15,Fscientific information on request."
OL,26,@oD@[OUwD@cO]
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
